Package Grupo11_ISCTE.Code_Smells_Detective

Class Detector

java.lang.Object
Grupo11_ISCTE.Code_Smells_Detective.Detector
public class Detector
extends java.lang.Object
Represents the Code Smells Detector. The Detector offers several methods to find code smells and calculate quality indicators of the detections made.
Since:
1.0
Version:
3.0
Author:
Marcelo Pereira
